        "created_at": "2021-05-19T10:56:19.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>One of the very best '11\u2019s I have had. It has enticing floral spice and a core of creamy, dark cherry. It is rich and layered with real depth and not the slightest bit of heaviness. It builds through the palate, fanning out on the finish and drives on and on. Brilliant!</p>",
